The best (but also rather expensive) outfit:
<br />

<br />
Jumpy Robe (36% Haste)
<br />
Silken Whip (Snare)
<br />
Di'Zok Shillagh (60% slow)
<br />

<br />
Equip a Frenzied Initiate (Tactics) with the above outfit and you will see the definition of : Carnage.
