<br />
I can help you with some of these. The summoned pets duel weild at a certain level (I forget which but look in the descriptions for animation spells on caster's realm). You can NOT get weapons back from summoned pets, but for charmed pets you can get them back by looting their dead corpse.
<br />

<br />
also, only certain kinds of mobs can weild weapons (eg: I don't think a sword does any good to a frog). I don't think it really matters on level.
<br />

