I dont believe this is the case. Example: I charmed a mature wurm in skyfire(wurm/dragon model so it walks on all fours) and handed it 2 mage swords. With Night's Dark Terror you can clearly see it weilding both swords, However when NDT wears off the model is unable to display the wurm weilding swords. If you watch the pet melee tho you will see "a mature wurm SLASHES" a whatever for whatever damage. Also the dragon's damage output did not seem to drop. Just because a model is unable to display weapons does not neccessarily mean it is not using them.
