                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Then it just matters what form the pet is in when you give weapons to it.  You will have to NDT some mobs to make them wield a weapon.  Because it is obvious that if you give them weapons in their natural form they will not use them (I know for sure imp models do this).
